<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>O, Kıeli Rýh ҮРәж144</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
.C       Am
 O Kıeli Rýh
.F            G
 Kelshi meniń tórime
.C           Am    F        G
 Taǵdyrymdy berdim Seniń erkińe
.C      Am
 Saǵan sendim
.F        G
 Saǵan berdim bárin de

[V2]
 O, Kıeli Rýh, bári Seniń qolyńda.
 Adamdyǵym, adaldyǵym, arym da.
 Bar kúnámdy qurban qyldym jolyńa.

[V3]
 Kel, Kıeli Rýh, januıama, balama,
 Sen joq jerde tynyshtyǵym bola ma?
 Óziń kelip uıalashy sanama.

[V4]
 O, Kıeli Rýh, kelshi meniń qazaǵyma.
 Tózip boldyq bul jalǵannyń mazaǵyna.
 Kúshińdi ber, shyǵar jalǵan azabynan</lyrics>
<key>C</key>
<author>Aqtanjanov S., Bolatov Q.</author>
<hymn_number>144</hymn_number>
</song>